CHAT SYSTEM
===========

The game has a multi-channel chat system for communicating with other
players. Chat history is saved, so you can catch up on messages even
if you were offline.

CHANNELS
--------
  chat  - Global in-character chat
  ooc   - Out-of-character discussions

CHANNEL COMMANDS
----------------
Each channel works the same way:
  <channel> <message>     - Send a message
  <channel> on            - Subscribe to channel
  <channel> off           - Unsubscribe from channel
  <channel> history [N]   - View last N messages (default 20)

Examples:
  chat Hello everyone!
  ooc Anyone know where the mages guild is?
  chat off
  ooc history 50

HISTORY COMMAND
---------------
The 'history' command can view history from any or all channels:
  history              - All channels, last 20 messages
  history 50           - All channels, last 50 messages
  history chat         - Chat channel only
  history ooc 30       - OOC channel, last 30 messages

OTHER COMMANDS
--------------
  channels   - List all channels and subscription status

Your subscription preferences are saved between sessions.

See also: chat (command), ooc, channels, history
